name: 9-11 Postage Stamp
description: It's not an anniversary, it is a memoriam. This stamp commemorates the 20 years that have lapsed since the World Trade Center attacks. I've always been a big fan of the lights that beam from the WTC site into space at night on the memoriam of 9-11. This postal stamp immortalizes that tribute. Created in 2021 by Nite Owl. @naitooru (twitter) @naito_oru (IG) 2400 x 3600 dpi png.
